Package: relayer
Type: Package
Title: Rethinking layers in 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c( 
    person("Claus O.", "Wilke", , "wilke@austin.utexas.edu", c("cre", "aut")))
Description: Layers are a core component of 'ggplot2', containing stats and geoms.
    This package allows novel manipulations of those layers. 
